description: Sivers Semiconductors AB engages in the development and manufacture of products for the data and telecommunication market as well as sensors to the industrial market. The company is headquartered in Kista, Stockholm and currently employs 104 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2011-05-30. Wireless develops RF chips and antennas for advanced 5G systems for data and telecommunications networks. Photonics develops and manufactures semiconductor-based optical products for optical fiber networks, sensors and optical fiber communications (Li-Fi).
naics: Semiconductor and Other Electronic Component Manufacturing
name: Sivers Semiconductors AB
